## Overview

Build a personal chatbot that answers questions **only about me**.

## Goals

* Accurate, concise answers about my background
* Strictly block unrelated questions
* Easy manual updates to personal data

## Non-Goals

* No user accounts or authentication
* No long-term chat memory
* No external knowledge beyond provided data

## Core Requirements

* Backend API for chat handling
* Clear fallback for out-of-scope questions

## Data Source

* Structured personal data (text file / Markdown): bio, skills, experience, projects, education, links
* Version-controlled and manually maintained

## AI Rules

* Use only provided data
* No guessing or hallucination
* Short, factual responses

## Tech & Security

* Single Next.js project (frontend + backend)
* Free-tier deployment (e.g. Vercel)
* Public API with CORS restricted to site domain

## Success Criteria

* Correct answers about me only
* Reliable performance on the website
